		<title>Nigerian Web3 startups raised $43 million in 2025, but growth remains early</title>
		<link>https://techcabal.com/2026/04/21/nigerias-web3-funding-rebounds/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Emmanuel Nwosu]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 18:08:51 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Funding]]></category>
