                    <h3 style="padding:0;width:100%;font-family:Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;font-weight:700;font-size:16px;color:#93888F;line-height:23.1px;text-align: left;margin:0;text-transform:uppercase">Startups</h3>
